{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b94c980693","title":"龙英华大字报五则","origin":"北京大学社会主义思想教育委员会编印《北京大学右派分子反动言论汇集》，一九五七年十月。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c1f1d184de","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":17,"articleId":"b94c980693"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"19f3f1b8ea","name":"北京大学"},{"id":"765ec99bb5","name":"龙英华"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"ad2b5c18b6","type":"title","text":"龙英华大字报五则","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b94c980693"},{"id":"fa29382faa","type":"authors","text":"北京大学龙英华","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b94c980693"},{"id":"fa0f4de158","type":"subtitle","text":"（龙英华：北京大学哲学系学生）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b94c980693"},{"id":"37f5adc294","type":"subtitle","text":"一、教条主义宣言","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b94c980693"},{"id":"2e85b1ba42","type":"paragraph","text":"一、“自由主义者”宣言是反宪法的，应该赶快撕。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b94c980693"},{"id":"9cb24828ea","type":"paragraph","text":"二、该宣言作者是反社会主义、反共产党、反中国的，应该逮捕法办。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b94c980693"},{"id":"84523c8823","type":"paragraph","text":"三、该宣言作者是杜勒斯的传声筒应该封闭。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b94c980693"},{"id":"774e0b4f41","type":"paragraph","text":"四、我——教条主义者就是能作以争鸣。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b94c980693"},{"id":"9f4e4cf1e6","type":"paragraph","text":"五、马克思主义者啊！我的老兄们，请你们救救社会主义的危机吧！咱们联合起来，改造自由主义者。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b94c980693"},{"id":"273e60ecbf","type":"paragraph","text":" 教条主义者：哲一　龙英华57．6．17．","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b94c980693"},{"id":"c537eec5a8","type":"subtitle","text":"二、评“致党委会”      哲一  龙英华","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b94c980693"},{"id":"729cbbbb5c","type":"paragraph","text":"1、“五·一九”以来，党委的领导还不坏，能跟着学生运动，不断向运动学习，不断纠正错误，不断进步，毕竟是领导好了运动。党委比南开的官僚主义者们高明多了，这不但要感谢党委的老英雄们，特别可能是要感谢党中央、毛主席和陆定一同志。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b94c980693"},{"id":"f0e0297682","type":"paragraph","text":"2、“五·一九”运动，是新的“五·四”运动，是现阶段的马克思主义启蒙运动，它是在“廿大”号召下产生的，它是在“匈牙利革命”（卡达尔领导工人阶级，推翻拉科西和西方反革命走狗）号召之下发生的，它是在我们的“人大”和英明的党中央和毛主席的一声炮响下发生的，毛主席的两个报告给我们送来了现阶段的马克思主义。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b94c980693"},{"id":"290c7122f0","type":"paragraph","text":"3、“五·一九”运动具有伟大的国内、国际意义。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b94c980693"},{"id":"8e049143e4","type":"subtitle","text":"三、北大当前社会主义民主运动中各派的初步分析草稿","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b94c980693"},{"id":"913ad0c3d5","type":"paragraph","text":"1、主观上大家一般是社会主义者，客观下有许多派别；","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b94c980693"},{"id":"02ba7f6aee","type":"paragraph","text":"2、","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b94c980693"},{"id":"cd278c154d","type":"paragraph","text":"①右倾冒险派：只要社会主义公有制，其他一切听便。","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b94c980693"},{"id":"89412445f8","type":"paragraph","text":"②进步派：拥护社会主义公有制，党中央、毛主席和绝大部分领导阶层。坚决要求实行真正的民主集中制。从根本上防止“三害”泛滥。","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b94c980693"},{"id":"c9611ef3c1","type":"paragraph","text":"③主力派：他们占大各数，他们中一部分已参战，一部分准备参战，一部分在观察。","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b94c980693"},{"id":"3e88629802","type":"paragraph","text":"④稳健派：他们暗中支持进步派，明中反冒险派。","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b94c980693"},{"id":"89cdf9ea82","type":"paragraph","text":"⑤保守派：他们站稳“立场”明中反对冒险派和进步派，暗中支持顽固派。","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b94c980693"},{"id":"2efaaa70e8","type":"paragraph","text":"⑥顽固派：坚决打击冒险派和进步派，欺骗主力派。","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b94c980693"},{"id":"077b4246c6","type":"paragraph","text":" 哲一：龙英华","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b94c980693"},{"id":"b61629c210","type":"subtitle","text":"四、反自由主义者宣言要点（共产主义者宣言要点）","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b94c980693"},{"id":"5cec1e2a75","type":"subtitle","text":"哲一  龙英华","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b94c980693"},{"id":"c992abd8bd","type":"paragraph","text":"1、中国公民中的自由主义者站到爱国主义的旗帜下来，共同反对殖民主义，爱国一家，我们都是革命的子孙。","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b94c980693"},{"id":"193bf777c2","type":"paragraph","text":"2、你自由主义者的宣言，具体反映了右派资产阶级的思想和愿望。中国工人和农民的愿望是同你们不同的。","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b94c980693"},{"id":"341ff8cc8a","type":"paragraph","text":"3、你在整风运动和社会主义民主运动中是一位不坏的教师。","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b94c980693"},{"id":"d90fc69ef5","type":"paragraph","text":"4、你是中国公民，你是个大学生，你有权利出来争鸣，欢迎你来争鸣。","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b94c980693"},{"id":"55d537d7ba","type":"paragraph","text":"5、马克思主义者对你的政策是利用、限制和改造。利用你的教师们用批判你的毒汁改造你自由主义者成为爱国主义者，第二步把你改造为社会主义者，如果你不太勉强的话。","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b94c980693"},{"id":"2d360dc82d","type":"paragraph","text":"6、你平日为人倒底怎样？","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b94c980693"},{"id":"311c472bc8","type":"paragraph","text":"7、把教条主义者改造成为马克思主义者。","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b94c980693"},{"id":"7092041514","type":"subtitle","text":"五、反教条主义的战友们","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b94c980693"},{"id":"42bff3cb02","type":"paragraph","text":"我建议组织一个全校性的、大型的“新三害”受害者诉苦大会，较彻底的扫除“新三害”，必需把整风运动推向新阶段。","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b94c980693"},{"id":"002402d129","type":"paragraph","text":" 龙英华  启","index":35,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b94c980693"}],"page":{"id":"a2daa47549","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b94c980693","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}